<h1 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h1>
<p>WalkieTalkie is a cross-platform push-to-talk (PTT) app. This chapter covers the desktop "Base Station" — the Go server app for Mac, Windows, and Linux — and the Android and iPhone apps. Android + Base Station are confirmed working together on real hardware. The iPhone app is in progress (buildable scaffold; device mesh verify pending).</p>


